Mentor is an equal opportunity employer and is committed to hiring a diverse workforce.

Notice to Recruiters & Agencies  

Mentor, a Siemens Business, prefers to recruit candidates directly, rather than through a third party recruiter or agency. Do not submit or present your candidates through any means (email, fax, phone, mail, verbal referral or any other means), to Mentor or any employee of Mentor. Mentor will only pay a fee for candidates submitted or presented after there is a signed recruiting agreement in place between Mentor and the recruiter or agency; and the candidate is submitted for a specific requisition. In the case of candidate(s) submitted or presented to Mentor by a recruiter or agency without a signed agreement in place or without a specific open requisition, Mentor explicitly reserves the right to pursue and hire those candidate(s) without any financial obligation to the recruiter or agency.
If you have a signed agreement with Mentor, please contact your Mentor staffing representative, who will provide you with the appropriate link to submit your candidates.




