Tanner EDA
Tanner AMS IC Design Flow
Affordable, integrated AMS design flow
Tanner AMS IC design flow supports analog/mixed-signal design in one highly-integrated, end-to-end flow. Engineers can perform top-down, mixed-signal simulation or co-simulation, synthesis with DFT support, place and route, and high-speed, “sign-off ready” timing analysis for tape-out, within one, cost-effective unified flow. Learn More
PCB Design, Analysis, & Package Integration
Xpedition Enterprise
Integrated printed circuit board software
Designing a product requires more than just a great PCB layout tool – you need tightly integrated PCB design software. Xpedition Enterprise provides tightly integrated PCB design software, enabling all team members to work collaboratively and more efficiently. Learn More


IC Design
Calibre nmDRC
Design rule checking that provides fast cycle times & innovative design rule capabilities
Total cycle time is on the rise due to more complex and larger designs, higher error counts and more verification iterations. Calibre® nmDRC responds to the need for reduced cycle time with revolutionary new capabilities that differentiate Calibre nmDRC substantially from traditional DRC tools. Learn More
Mechanical Analysis
FloEFD
An evolution in Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD), Engineering Fluid Dynamics (EFD)
Tightly integrated with major MCAD systems including Pro/ENGINEER, SolidWorks, and CATIA, FloEFD is fully-featured 3D fluid flow and heat transfer analysis software without the numerical complexity and meshing overhead of traditional CFD. Learn More











