The fastest CFD solution from MCAD model to manufactured product. FloEFD is a full-featured 3D computational fluid dynamics analysis solution built into major MCAD systems such as Creo, CATIA V5, Siemens NX and SolidWorks. It tightly integrates with Inventor and SolidEdge.
		
