          Mentor Graphics Corporation

 
Mentor Graphics Corporation









Overview


Products







    Partner Information


Mentor®, a Siemens Business, is a world leader in electronic software and hardware design solutions, providing products, consulting services and award-winning support for the world’s most successful electronic, semiconductor and systems companies. The company offers innovative products and solutions that help engineers overcome the design challenges they face in the increasingly complex worlds of board, chip and software design. The Mentor Embedded Systems Division enables embedded development for a variety of applications including automotive, industrial, medical, internet of things, wearables, smart energy, and consumer electronics. Embedded developers can create systems with the latest SoCs and MPSoCs from Xilinx and Mentor’s commercially supported and customizable solutions.  Using the Mentor Embedded Multicore Framework (MEMF), multiple operating systems can be hosted on a single Xilinx device, maximizing available hardware resources and managing secure domain separation.  The Mentor solution suite includes the Eclipse-based industry-leading Sourcery CodeBench with Sourcery Analyzer visual profiling tool, Yocto Project-based Mentor Embedded Linux, Android, and Mentor’s real-time operating system Nucleus RTOS.  Found in more than 3 billion devices worldwide, Nucleus SafetyCert is safety-certified and has been optimized for Xilinx platforms, allowing developers to take advantage of its small footprint.






